<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="state-vt">state <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /steɪt/    美 /steɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>陈述；说明</strong></h4>
<p>to say or write sth, especially formally：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He stated that Olympians had brought joy to people across the world.
他说奥运选手给全世界人民带来了欢乐。</p><footer>译林④ – 2</footer></div></div>